--- RESULT ---
All 6 pages of the **Quantum Flux PhoneHub** website are built in `demos/e-quantum-flux/`:

**Pages delivered:**

| Page | File | Key Features |
|------|------|-------------|
| Home | `index.html` (17.5 KB) | 3 animated aurora blobs, typing subtitle, 6 product cards with animated gradient borders, 12 brand tiles, 3 news cards, stats section |
| Explore | `search.html` (15.4 KB) | Sidebar with brand accordion/price slider/rating filters, sort dropdown, all 12 products, filter chips |
| Brands | `brands.html` (12 KB) | Category tabs, 173 brands (Mobiles 32, Auto 128, Laptops 8, TVs 5), glassmorphism tiles with counters |
| Product | `product.html` (20.4 KB) | Breadcrumb, gradient-bordered hero, 6 key spec cards, collapsible full specs table, AI Review with scores, Where to Buy, 4 related products |
| Compare | `compare.html` (19.6 KB) | Product selector dropdown (all 12), comparison table with cyan winner highlighting, dual summary cards, overall winner announcement |
| News | `news.html` (15.4 KB) | Category filter tabs, 9 article cards, trending section (main + sidebar), newsletter signup |

**Quantum Flux aesthetic throughout:**
- Deep indigo `#0c0f1e` base, electric violet/cyan gradient text and borders
- Glassmorphism cards (`backdrop-filter: blur(16px)`, `rgba(255,255,255,0.05)`)
- Animated gradient borders (violet→cyan flowing via `@keyframes borderFlow`)
- Magnetic cursor tilt on all product/brand/spec cards (JS `mousemove` tracking)
- IntersectionObserver scroll animations (slide-in + scale-up + staggered delays)
- Aurora/nebula blobs + morphing mesh blobs
- `prefers-reduced-motion` support
- All pages interlinked via consistent sticky header + footer navigation
